 very happy to give you information about the next two workshops.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-2-part-1-2023-08-02-09-32-11/47.mp3","time_start":145.12,"time_end":149.67},{"position":48,"content":"On Saturday the 16th, there's Building Castles.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-2-part-1-2023-08-02-09-32-11/48.mp3","time_start":149.89,"time_end":154.71},{"position":49,"content":"Oh, sounds great!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-2-part-1-2023-08-02-09-32-11/49.mp3","time_start":154.71,"time_end":156.64},{"position":50,"content":"This involves quite a bit of glue, so just make sure the kids are in old clothes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-2-part-1-2023-08-02-09-32-11/50.mp3","time_start":156.64,"time_end":162.22},{"position":51,"content":"I know, ones I don't mind getting mucky.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-2-part-1-2023-08-02-09-32-11/51.mp3","time_start":162.22,"time_end":165.23},{"position":52,"content":"Exactly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-2-part-1-2023-08-02-09-32-11/52.mp3","time_start":165.38,"time_end":166.51},{"position":53,"content":"And if possible, could you bring along bottle tops","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-2-part-1-2023-08-02-09-32-11/53.mp3","time_start":166.63,"time_end":170.19},{"position":54,"content":"which the children might be able to use in the models, you know, as decoration?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-2-part-1-2023-08-02-09-32-11/54.mp3","time_start":170.19,"time_end":174.43},{"position":55,"content":"We'll certainly try to find some for you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/iel